item.title: Euryomyrtus ramosissima subsp. prostrata
item.dc:creator: linleymcg
item.description: Tiny prostate plant with tiny flowers (about 7-8mm diam) which face downwards. Woody stem. Observed Sept to Nov.

item.title: Daviesia arenaria
item.dc:creator: linleymcg
item.description: Daviesia arenaria because of the colour of the flower and the ‘folded’ phyllodes.

item.title: Stylidium calcaratum spp. agg.
item.dc:creator: linleymcg
item.description: White form also observed in the general area.
